query:
SELECT er.id, er.employeeId, e.name as employee_name, er.requestType, er.vacationType, er.vacationStartDate, er.vacationEndDate, er.status
FROM employeeRequests er
JOIN employees e ON er.employeeId = e.id
WHERE er.requestType = 'vacation' AND er.status = 'approved'
ORDER BY er.vacationStartDate DESC
LIMIT 10;
